        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is included in an Envato Elements subscription?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "An Envato Elements subscription gives you unlimited downloads of 28+ million creative assets, including stock photos, stock video, video templates, music, sound effects, graphics, 3D assets, fonts, and add-ons. It also includes access to AI tools for generating images, video, voice over, music, and graphics — with usage limits depending on your plan tier.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can I use Envato Elements assets for commercial projects?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. Every asset you download from Envato Elements comes with a lifetime commercial license. You can use them in client work, YouTube videos, merchandise, advertising, and more. The license covers assets you've already downloaded even if you cancel your subscription later.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How much does Envato Elements cost?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The Core plan starts at $16.50 per month when billed annually (or $39/month billed monthly). The Plus plan is $39/month billed annually and includes 100 AI generations. The Ultimate plan is $109/month billed annually with expanded AI usage. All plans include unlimited downloads of the full asset library.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Envato Elements worth it for freelancers?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. For freelancers who regularly need stock footage, music, templates, or graphics, Envato Elements typically pays for itself within the first project. A single premium stock video or music track on other marketplaces can cost $15–$80, while an entire month of unlimited downloads on Envato Elements starts at $16.50.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
